    ID           shift, and go to state 12
    NOT          shift, and go to state 13
    ADD          shift, and go to state 14
    SUB          shift, and go to state 15
    SEMI         shift, and go to state 16
    LP           shift, and go to state 17
    LBRACE       shift, and go to state 18

    stmt                 go to state 110
    type_specifier       go to state 22
    declaration          go to state 23
    compound_stmt        go to state 24
    expr_stmt            go to state 25
    select_stmt          go to state 26
    iter_stmt            go to state 27
    jump_stmt            go to state 28
    expression           go to state 29
    assign_expr          go to state 30
    logic_or_expr        go to state 31
    logic_and_expr       go to state 32
    equality_expr        go to state 33
    relational_expr      go to state 34
    additive_expr        go to state 35
    multiplicative_expr  go to state 36
    unary_expr           go to state 37
    primary_expr         go to state 38


state 108

    1 program: MAIN LP RP LBRACE stmt_list RBRACE .

    $default  reduce using rule 1 (program)


state 109

   28 select_stmt: IF LP expression RP stmt ELSE stmt .

    $default  reduce using rule 28 (select_stmt)


state 110

   30 iter_stmt: FOR LP expr_stmt expr_stmt expression RP stmt .

    $default  reduce using rule 30 (iter_stmt)
